### Phase 2: Reliability & Performance\
\
#### 2.1 Add Response Caching\
**Files:** New `shellwise/cache.py`\
- JSONL cache at `~/.shellwise/cache.jsonl`\
- Key = hash(cwd + normalized_query)\
- TTL: 24h for READ commands, 1h for WRITE commands\
- Auto-refresh cached plan if execution fails\
- Sanitize sensitive data (passwords, tokens, API keys)\
- **Reference:** `TermCoach/src/core/cache.ts`\
\
#### 2.2 Improve Model Query Reliability\
**Files:** `shellwise/model.py`, `shellwise/ai.py`\
- Add retry logic for transient failures\
- Support model fallback list (try next model on timeout/429)\
- Use `llama_cpp.Llama.create_chat_completion()` properly (already done)\
- Better JSON extraction with regex (already done)\
- **Reference:** `TermCoach/src/core/interpreter.ts` lines 209-331\
\
#### 2.3 Richer Shell Context\
**Files:** `shellwise/ai.py`\
- Include `ls -la` output (first 50 lines) in system prompt\
- Detect git branch and dirty status\
