- Include recent command history (last 10)\
- **Reference:** `TermCoach/src/core/context.ts`\
\
#### 2.4 Safer Command Execution\
**Files:** `shellwise/executor.py`\
- Use `subprocess.Popen` with arg arrays for simple commands (no `shell=True`)\
- Only use shell mode for commands with pipes/globs/redirections\
- Proper timeout handling\
- **Reference:** `TermCoach/src/core/executor.ts`\
